Blue metal
In order to acquire another rare specimen of the giant predatory bug, Rindeil needs a meteorite sample which is now in the possession of the Khadagan army and held in one of their camps.
#subobj 1
Get behind the gates
The new barracks are located further south of the Black Market. Although the gates are hardly protected, be vigilant.
#subobj 2
Open the chest
The meteorite samples are in a chest, but only an experienced thief will be able to open it.
#subobj 3
Come back alive!
Now you need to hide until the theft is detected and a chase is initiated.
